                       <p>The Internship and Career Services Centre at the National School of Journalism, Bangalore (NSoJ) offers valuable resources to help you at every stage of your career. </p>
 
                        <p>Experienced industry professionals advise students on a wide range of career development topics, including resumes, interviews, conducting a search, networking and selecting references. We connect students with prospective employers through our internship programme. We place our students at leading media organisations across India in a month-long mandatory internship programme. Student select the organisation for their internship during month three of the programme. All of our current students have had a wide range of oppurtunities to choose from and have been placed at prestigious organisations, including The Times of India and NDTV for their internship. </p>
                        
