                        <p>Our selective admissions process, small class size, tremendous opportunities for skills, essentials and practical development and unparalleled industry connections ensure that our students receive the most meaningful and lucrative entry job offers in the Indian media industry. Our graduates will go on to work for India's leading newspapers, magazines, blogs, television and radio channels, as well as advertising agencies. Several of our students may also choose to start their careers within corporate communications departments of large Indian and multinational corporations.</p>
                         
